            bindings = <
        &kp EXCL    &kp AT            &kp HASH         &kp DLLR       &kp PRCNT    &kp CARET  &kp AMPS   &kp ASTERISK  &kp LEFT_PARENTHESIS  &kp RIGHT_PARENTHESIS
        &trans      &trans            &kp PRINTSCREEN  &kp PAGE_UP    &trans       &kp LEFT   &kp DOWN   &kp UP        &kp RIGHT             &kp SQT
&trans  &kp C_PREV  &kp C_PLAY_PAUSE  &kp C_NEXT       &kp PAGE_DOWN  &trans       &kp BSLH   &kp MINUS  &kp EQUAL     &kp LBKT              &kp RBKT               &trans
